name: M.A.C Cosmetics Strobe Dewy Skin Tint
description:
Lightweight coverage meets a luminous glow with M.A.C Cosmetics Strobe Dewy Skin Tint. This tinted moisturiser takes the beautifully lit-from-within finish of the cult favourite Strobe Cream and combines it with sheer yet buildable coverage and a skincare-infused formula.

Why will I love M.A.C Cosmetics Strobe Dewy Skin Tint?

  • Tinted moisturiser with a dewy, luminous finish
  • Ideal for normal to dry skin types
  • Pearlescent, light-reflecting finish
  • Sheer, buildable coverage
  • Wears for 8 hours
  • Colour-true and non-fading for 8 hours
  • Hydrating, comfortable feel
  • Formulated with hyaluronic acid, vitamin E, shea butter and squalane
  • Contains 78.65% skincare ingredients
  • 74% naturally derived ingredients
  • 30ml

MAC Cosmetics Strobe Dewy Skin Tint leaves skin with a lightweight, pearlescent finish, while the gel-balm texture feels comfortable. Hyaluronic acid, shea butter and squalane hydrate and nourish skin, while antioxidant Vitamin E helps protect against environmental aggressors.

How to apply MAC Cosmetics Strobe Dewy Skin Tint:

Apply to clean skin with fingertips, a sponge or a brush. Build as needed for more coverage.MAC Cosmetics Strobe Dewy Skin Tint can be worn alone for a dewy glow, under foundation for subtle radiance or under powder for a matte yet radiant look.
